1
02:54:59,979 --> 02:55:02,980
I will not part with...
...a single coin.

2
02:55:03,659 --> 02:55:06,185
Not one piece of it.

3
02:55:10,059 --> 02:55:12,385
My teeth... are swords.

4
02:55:13,259 --> 02:55:16,581
My claws are spears.

5
02:55:18,699 --> 02:55:19,860
My Wings...

6
02:55:20,499 --> 02:55:23,025
are a hurricane.

7
02:55:28,659 --> 02:55:30,502
So it is true.

8
02:55:30,859 --> 02:55:33,021
The Black Arrow found its mark.

9
02:55:33,259 --> 02:55:34,181
What did you say?

10
02:55:35,019 --> 02:55:38,910
I was just saying your reputation
precedes you, O Smaug...

11
02:55:39,139 --> 02:55:40,345
the Tyrannical.

12
02:55:40,939 --> 02:55:42,020
Truly.

13
02:55:42,259 --> 02:55:44,227
You have no equal on this earth.

14
02:55:48,659 --> 02:55:49,308
I am...

15
02:55:49,579 --> 02:55:52,822
almost tempted to let you take it.

